cs.CV, cs.EM, cs.AR, cs.LG, cs.AI 

This paper is primarily focused on computer vision and the energy efficiency of different algorithms for embedded vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). Additionally, the paper discusses the energy consumption of the algorithms, which could fall under cs.EM (Embedded Systems) or cs.AR (Hardware Architecture). The paper also compares the performance of deep learning algorithms to traditional hand-crafted approaches, which could fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
